        },
        "text_eYUdQq": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "t:names.text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We believe good design should have a place in everyday life. For us, thoughtful pricing is part of that. </p><p>We want our prices to feel considered and honest, reflecting the object, the work behind it, and the care involved in bringing it to you. The value should be in what you receive, not in an inflated brand premium or exclusivity for its own sake.</p>",
